  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Trial of Flexible Doses of Oral Ziprasidone in Children and Adolescents With Bipolar I Disorder</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Multicenter, Four-week, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group Efficacy And Safety Trial Of Flexible Doses Of Oral Ziprasidone In Children And Adolescents With Bipolar I Disorder (Current Or Most Recent Episode Manic)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
